1
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:57,520
Mutou.

2
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:06,960
Oh no.

3
00:02:07,360 --> 00:02:09,090
How do I piece it back together?

4
00:02:10,639 --> 00:02:13,200
Right, there seem to be words on the back.

5
00:02:23,280 --> 00:02:24,680
In the future, I

6
00:02:25,079 --> 00:02:25,760
wish...

7
00:02:26,760 --> 00:02:27,640
Wish I...

8
00:02:29,640 --> 00:02:30,760
Wish I what?

9
00:02:31,600 --> 00:02:34,000
It should be some kind of blessing.

10
00:02:35,440 --> 00:02:37,900
Wish I live as long as the Southern Mountain.

11
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:38,880
Wish I

12
00:02:39,440 --> 00:02:40,900
eat a lot but never get fat.

13
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:43,130
Wish I become more and more beautiful.

14
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:48,000
If he finds out

15
00:02:48,079 --> 00:02:50,040
that the gift he carefully picked for me

16
00:02:50,040 --> 00:02:51,500
was ruined by me like this,

17
00:02:52,120 --> 00:02:53,720
he will definitely be angry.

18
00:02:57,920 --> 00:02:59,880
What exactly is in here?

19
00:03:04,640 --> 00:03:06,970
Now this secret has truly become a secret.

20
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:10,240
Forget it.

21
00:03:11,200 --> 00:03:12,330
Since it's a secret,

22
00:03:12,760 --> 00:03:14,640
let it be a secret forever.

23
00:03:15,320 --> 00:03:16,680
I can't possibly go ask him

24
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:18,160
what is written inside.

25
00:03:19,720 --> 00:03:21,250
Wouldn't that give me away?

26
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:22,600
No way.

27
00:03:24,160 --> 00:03:25,360
I just won't tell him.

28
00:03:28,640 --> 00:03:29,560
I wonder if

29
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:31,880
she has looked at the puzzle.

30
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:35,180
Goodbye, Grandma.

31
00:03:35,960 --> 00:03:37,360
Goodbye. Take care.

32
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:43,560
Grandma,

33
00:03:44,040 --> 00:03:45,600
where did Yuanbao go then?

34
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:47,690
She didn't call you?

35
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:51,000
She said she'll be studying at the library these days.

36
00:03:52,079 --> 00:03:53,740
I happen to be going there too.

37
00:03:54,600 --> 00:03:55,040
Well,

38
00:03:55,079 --> 00:03:56,040
Grandma, you should go back inside.

39
00:03:56,040 --> 00:03:56,800
Okay.

40
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:02,280
Is she going with Meng Jingu?

41
00:04:30,960 --> 00:04:32,220
Do you know how to work?

42
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:34,480
What are your big eyes for?

43
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:35,960
Look at all this fog.

44
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:37,880
Here, there, it's all fog.

45
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:39,159
Wipe it over there.

46
00:04:39,720 --> 00:04:41,050
I'll wipe it right away.

47
00:04:47,760 --> 00:04:48,480
Why are you

48
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:50,120
so clumsy?

49
00:04:50,320 --> 00:04:51,680
Can't you even mop the floor properly?

50
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:52,840
Spilling everything everywhere.

51
00:04:52,840 --> 00:04:54,080
Do you like wiping?

52
00:05:45,640 --> 00:05:46,200
Go away!

53
00:05:46,200 --> 00:05:46,840
Dad!

54
00:05:48,760 --> 00:05:49,640
Sorry.

55
00:05:49,840 --> 00:05:50,880
I thought you were a bad guy.

56
00:05:50,880 --> 00:05:52,760
I saw a little girl walking alone at night.

57
00:05:52,760 --> 00:05:53,520
I'm sorry.

58
00:05:54,040 --> 00:05:54,800
It's okay.

59
00:05:55,080 --> 00:05:56,560
You are quite strong.

60
00:05:56,720 --> 00:05:57,920
I'm sorry.

61
00:05:58,440 --> 00:06:00,080
Why didn't you wait for me after school?

62
00:06:00,080 --> 00:06:02,120
I saw you were too busy with work.

63
00:06:02,200 --> 00:06:03,460
I can go back by myself.

64
00:06:04,280 --> 00:06:05,680
My daughter has grown up.

65
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:07,760
But Dad still worries about you.

66
00:06:08,080 --> 00:06:09,160
Let's go home.

67
00:06:09,320 --> 00:06:11,160
Your mom made delicious food for you.

68
00:06:11,160 --> 00:06:11,800
Really?

69
00:06:11,880 --> 00:06:13,080
Let me guess.

70
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:14,960
Ribs or braised fish?

71
00:06:15,160 --> 00:06:16,000
Both.

72
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:44,760
My three lovely fairies.

73
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:46,130
Good morning to you all.

74
00:06:46,360 --> 00:06:48,159
Everyone will have to work hard again today.

75
00:06:48,159 --> 00:06:50,480
But we still need to do our best.

76
00:06:51,280 --> 00:06:52,760
If you...

77
00:06:52,880 --> 00:06:55,159
If you are tired, we can take turns resting.

78
00:06:55,159 --> 00:06:56,480
You can call me anytime.

79
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:58,409
I'd be happy to take turns with you.

80
00:06:59,120 --> 00:07:00,320
Always remember

81
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:03,880
that we will always be a family.

82
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:06,040
Let's do our best!

83
00:07:11,080 --> 00:07:13,080
What's wrong with him today?

84
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:14,440
Is he crazy?

85
00:07:24,080 --> 00:07:25,360
Spare my life, young hero.

86
00:07:25,360 --> 00:07:26,600
Let's talk this out.

87
00:07:27,640 --> 00:07:30,040
Is being a bubble tea shop manager such a big deal?

88
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:30,720
If you ever dare

89
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:32,960
to boss your employees around again,

90
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:34,700
I'll make sure you can't walk.

91
00:07:34,880 --> 00:07:37,560
If you want to play the big boss, I'll leave you bedridden.

92
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:39,240
I-I'll never do it again.

93
00:07:39,280 --> 00:07:40,200
Never again.

94
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:42,200
It hurts.

95
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:30,400
Shang Ningyu.

96
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:36,840
Yuanbao,

97
00:08:36,880 --> 00:08:38,200
Auntie, where is Mutou?

98
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:39,559
Weren't you two going to attend

99
00:08:39,559 --> 00:08:41,080
your classmate's birthday?

100
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:42,409
Yes. Did he leave first?

101
00:08:43,159 --> 00:08:45,160
This kid. Why didn't he wait for you?

102
00:08:45,560 --> 00:08:47,200
It's fine. I'll go by myself.

103
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:50,400
Then be safe on the road, Yuanbao.

104
00:08:50,840 --> 00:08:51,720
Okay.

105
00:08:52,480 --> 00:08:53,320
This kid.

106
00:08:55,480 --> 00:08:56,040
Bro,

107
00:08:56,560 --> 00:08:58,760
you're doing this to let Yuanbao relax.

108
00:08:59,120 --> 00:09:01,120
But you're making me bleed out.

109
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:07,160
I might not even have enough for food.

110
00:09:07,760 --> 00:09:08,620
How much short?

111
00:09:09,880 --> 00:09:11,080
Three hundred.

112
00:09:23,400 --> 00:09:24,730
Don't tell anyone else.

113
00:09:24,920 --> 00:09:25,760
Don't worry, bro.

114
00:09:25,760 --> 00:09:27,400
My mouth is like a safe,

115
00:09:27,480 --> 00:09:28,200
so tight

116
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:30,130
it doesn't even let air out.

117
00:09:32,160 --> 00:09:33,720
Doesn't let air out, huh?

118
00:09:34,600 --> 00:09:35,560
My mom fed me

119
00:09:35,560 --> 00:09:37,490
a lot of sweet potatoes last night.

120
00:09:38,400 --> 00:09:39,200
Sorry, bro.

121
00:09:47,160 --> 00:09:48,280
Hubby, here.

122
00:09:50,040 --> 00:09:51,760
Jingu, are you going out?

123
00:09:52,520 --> 00:09:53,780
I have something to do.

124
00:09:57,600 --> 00:09:58,400
Good morning.

125
00:09:58,800 --> 00:10:00,080
Good morning, Uncle and Aunt.

126
00:10:00,080 --> 00:10:01,520
Xinrui, come in.

127
00:10:02,400 --> 00:10:03,800
Xinrui, why

128
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:05,160
are you here?

129
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:08,160
Didn't I tell you I was going out today?

130
00:10:08,560 --> 00:10:10,440
I was bored staying home alone.

131
00:10:10,800 --> 00:10:12,860
Where are you going? Take me with you.

132
00:10:14,200 --> 00:10:16,000
It's not very convenient for me.

133
00:10:16,320 --> 00:10:18,780
You used to take me with you when you went out.

134
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:20,560
Just let me go with you.

135
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:23,080
Exactly.

136
00:10:23,400 --> 00:10:24,600
Xinrui just came back.

137
00:10:24,600 --> 00:10:26,000
You should take her out more.

138
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:27,320
I'm not going out for fun.

139
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:28,520
I really have something to do.

140
00:10:28,520 --> 00:10:31,040
What important things could a student like you have to do?

141
00:10:31,040 --> 00:10:32,280
No matter where you go today,

142
00:10:32,280 --> 00:10:33,560
you must take Xinrui with you.

143
00:10:33,560 --> 00:10:34,560
Otherwise, you can't go either.

144
00:10:34,560 --> 00:10:35,280
You guys...

145
00:10:41,880 --> 00:10:43,560
Jingu, just listen to me.

146
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:46,820
Don't you still want to buy that medical insurance?

147
00:10:49,960 --> 00:10:52,000
Please, take me with you.

148
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:52,960
I promise.

149
00:10:53,520 --> 00:10:54,440
I won't bother you.

150
00:10:54,440 --> 00:10:56,080
I'll just stay quiet, okay?

151
00:10:56,960 --> 00:10:57,600
Son.

152
00:10:59,880 --> 00:11:01,960
Come on, eat and drink whatever you want.

153
00:11:01,960 --> 00:11:02,720
Today,

154
00:11:03,720 --> 00:11:04,520
it's my treat.

155
00:11:05,440 --> 00:11:07,240
Come on, brother. Let me toast you first.

156
00:11:07,240 --> 00:11:09,680
It's been eight cans, serve some food.

157
00:11:09,800 --> 00:11:11,000
I'm so full.

158
00:11:11,040 --> 00:11:12,680
Let's drink first.

159
00:11:12,880 --> 00:11:14,520
I can't swallow it anymore.

160
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:16,040
Have another drink. Have another drink.

161
00:11:16,040 --> 00:11:17,080
When will the hot dishes be served?

162
00:11:17,080 --> 00:11:18,680
Wait a minute. Wait a minute.

163
00:11:18,920 --> 00:11:19,780
Still waiting?

164
00:11:21,880 --> 00:11:23,440
What time is it now?

165
00:11:23,800 --> 00:11:24,640
Wait a little longer.

166
00:11:24,640 --> 00:11:26,570
I really can't swallow it anymore.

167
00:11:30,280 --> 00:11:31,440
Yuanbao, over here.

168
00:11:34,120 --> 00:11:35,580
Everyone is here so early.

169
00:11:35,840 --> 00:11:37,760
We're all waiting for you. Hurry up.

170
00:11:37,760 --> 00:11:39,090
Yuanbao, come sit here.

171
00:11:39,800 --> 00:11:40,360
Move over.

172
00:11:40,360 --> 00:11:41,890
We've been waiting for you.

173
00:11:43,080 --> 00:11:45,480
Then let's start.

174
00:11:46,640 --> 00:11:47,160
Come on.

175
00:11:47,800 --> 00:11:49,260
I'm lighting the candles.

176
00:11:51,280 --> 00:11:57,760
Happy birthday to you.

177
00:11:58,120 --> 00:12:01,360
Happy birthday to you.

178
00:12:01,720 --> 00:12:04,960
Happy birthday to you.

179
00:12:05,200 --> 00:12:07,040
Happy birthday.

180
00:12:09,600 --> 00:12:10,800
Thank you, everyone.

181
00:12:11,080 --> 00:12:13,280
It's so great to have you all here.

182
00:12:14,360 --> 00:12:16,160
Happy birthday to my little brother.

183
00:12:16,160 --> 00:12:18,420
May you get beaten less by Mom from now on.

184
00:12:18,480 --> 00:12:19,960
Bro, what are you saying?

185
00:12:20,600 --> 00:12:24,000
Shang Ningyu, I wish all your dreams come true.

186
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:25,920
That's a great wish from Ruirui.

187
00:12:27,120 --> 00:12:29,040
I wish you speak with eloquence

188
00:12:29,120 --> 00:12:30,650
and stop talking nonsense.

189
00:12:31,480 --> 00:12:32,560
Xiong Yuanbao,

190
00:12:32,640 --> 00:12:34,640
I found that you have learned bad things now.

191
00:12:34,640 --> 00:12:35,720
It's my turn.

192
00:12:36,640 --> 00:12:37,900
I wish you, my brother,

193
00:12:38,080 --> 00:12:39,560
a very happy birthday,

194
00:12:39,680 --> 00:12:41,600
never to return,

195
00:12:41,640 --> 00:12:42,720
and gone.

196
00:12:42,720 --> 00:12:43,120
Once you go,

197
00:12:43,120 --> 00:12:44,600
it's all over.

198
00:12:44,720 --> 00:12:45,320
Alright.

199
00:12:45,360 --> 00:12:46,640
Smooth sailing!

200
00:12:48,480 --> 00:12:49,280
Shang Ningyu,

201
00:12:49,320 --> 00:12:51,380
wish you good health and all the best.

202
00:12:51,480 --> 00:12:52,560
Thank you, class monitor.

203
00:12:52,560 --> 00:12:53,560
Success in your studies!

204
00:12:53,560 --> 00:12:54,160
Thank you.

205
00:12:54,600 --> 00:12:57,040
You guys have said almost all the good words,

206
00:12:57,040 --> 00:12:58,370
and left nothing for me.

207
00:12:59,200 --> 00:13:00,440
Then, I wish...

208
00:13:00,480 --> 00:13:01,280
Got it.

209
00:13:02,480 --> 00:13:03,240
Got it, bro.

210
00:13:03,280 --> 00:13:05,280
Longevity and good fortune, right?

211
00:13:05,600 --> 00:13:06,240
I get you.

212
00:13:07,200 --> 00:13:08,000
Shang Ningyu,

213
00:13:09,280 --> 00:13:10,320
happy birthday.

214
00:13:11,520 --> 00:13:14,440
I hope all of us good friends

215
00:13:14,520 --> 00:13:16,640
can always be by your side.

216
00:13:17,320 --> 00:13:18,450
Thank you, Qiao Yan.

217
00:13:18,480 --> 00:13:20,240
It's great that you could come.

218
00:13:20,600 --> 00:13:21,400
Thanks.

219
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:24,720
Is everyone here?

220
00:13:24,760 --> 00:13:25,820
Let's cut the cake.

221
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:26,760
Time to cut the cake.

222
00:13:26,760 --> 00:13:28,960
Cut the cake. Cut the cake. Cut the cake.

223
00:13:29,440 --> 00:13:31,080
Didn't you invite someone else?

224
00:13:31,080 --> 00:13:31,760
Who?

225
00:13:32,400 --> 00:13:33,440
Right, right, right.

226
00:13:33,440 --> 00:13:34,640
I invited Meng Jingu.

227
00:13:34,720 --> 00:13:36,040
Look at my memory.

228
00:13:36,120 --> 00:13:37,840
I even forgot the person I invited.

229
00:13:37,840 --> 00:13:39,840
Let's wait a little longer.

230
00:13:43,040 --> 00:13:44,880
Cheers, cheers, cheers.

231
00:13:47,760 --> 00:13:48,320
Jingu.

232
00:13:48,360 --> 00:13:49,290
Happy birthday.

233
00:13:49,480 --> 00:13:50,480
Hello, everyone.

234
00:13:54,760 --> 00:13:55,880
Xinrui is here too.

235
00:13:56,160 --> 00:13:56,760
Well,

236
00:13:57,600 --> 00:13:58,800
have a seat.

237
00:14:00,240 --> 00:14:00,800
Sit down.

238
00:14:03,880 --> 00:14:04,360
Xinrui,

239
00:14:04,440 --> 00:14:05,800
come and sit here.

240
00:14:05,880 --> 00:14:07,200
Sit here.

241
00:14:07,320 --> 00:14:07,920
Okay.

242
00:14:11,240 --> 00:14:12,920
Happy birthday, Shang Ningyu.

243
00:14:12,920 --> 00:14:15,520
I heard from Jingu that it's your birthday today.

244
00:14:15,520 --> 00:14:17,280
But I didn't know what you liked.

245
00:14:17,280 --> 00:14:17,680
No need.

246
00:14:17,680 --> 00:14:18,680
So I brought this,

247
00:14:18,800 --> 00:14:20,560
an album signed by Jay Chou.

248
00:14:20,600 --> 00:14:21,330
It's for you.

249
00:14:23,960 --> 00:14:25,320
This...

250
00:14:25,360 --> 00:14:29,600
It's really an album signed by Jay Chou.

251
00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:30,800
Yeah.

252
00:14:31,920 --> 00:14:34,400
My uncle's friend organizes concerts,

253
00:14:34,440 --> 00:14:36,170
and got it specifically for me.

254
00:14:36,480 --> 00:14:37,160
Bro.

255
00:14:37,480 --> 00:14:40,840
I figured this birthday of yours is totally worth it.

256
00:14:41,200 --> 00:14:42,560
You hit the jackpot.

257
00:14:43,200 --> 00:14:45,080
Xinrui, you are too kind.

258
00:14:45,560 --> 00:14:46,800
Well, I know.

259
00:14:47,760 --> 00:14:48,680
I just got here,

260
00:14:48,800 --> 00:14:50,800
so we might not be very familiar yet.

261
00:14:51,480 --> 00:14:53,480
Before I came, I was afraid

262
00:14:53,480 --> 00:14:55,140
I would spoil everyone's fun.

263
00:14:55,400 --> 00:14:56,960
I hope you don't mind.

264
00:14:57,400 --> 00:14:58,640
Not at all.

265
00:14:58,720 --> 00:14:59,760
Why would we mind?

266
00:14:59,800 --> 00:15:00,600
Of course not.

267
00:15:01,760 --> 00:15:02,560
That's great.

268
00:15:03,200 --> 00:15:05,560
Yuanbao, you don't mind either, do you?

269
00:15:08,480 --> 00:15:09,880
Why would I mind?

270
00:15:10,520 --> 00:15:11,850
I'm glad you could come.

271
00:15:12,400 --> 00:15:13,600
I was actually afraid

272
00:15:13,640 --> 00:15:15,560
you would misunderstand me

273
00:15:15,760 --> 00:15:17,640
because of the notebook incident.

274
00:15:17,640 --> 00:15:19,440
I wouldn't. It's in the past.

275
00:15:21,600 --> 00:15:22,200
By the way.

276
00:15:22,760 --> 00:15:25,040
I know you all like Jay Chou,

277
00:15:25,240 --> 00:15:27,880
so I got a few extras for you guys.

278
00:15:27,920 --> 00:15:28,240
Thank you.

279
00:15:28,240 --> 00:15:29,280
I hope you like them.

280
00:15:29,280 --> 00:15:31,680
Thank you. I don't like Jay Chou's songs.

281
00:15:33,720 --> 00:15:34,440
I like them.

282
00:15:36,440 --> 00:15:37,040
Thank you.

283
00:15:37,560 --> 00:15:38,760
This is for you.

284
00:15:39,480 --> 00:15:40,880
I don't like them either.

285
00:15:42,120 --> 00:15:44,050
Bro, you like them. Did you forget?

286
00:15:44,520 --> 00:15:45,320
Take it away.

287
00:15:49,160 --> 00:15:49,960
Ruirui.

288
00:15:59,880 --> 00:16:00,520
Yuanbao.

289
00:16:01,120 --> 00:16:01,760
Thank you.

290
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:04,160
Thank you. Thank you. Thank you.

291
00:16:04,160 --> 00:16:06,160
I gave it to Jingu's family already.

292
00:16:08,120 --> 00:16:08,840
I know.

293
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:12,260
You all probably don't know me very well.

294
00:16:12,320 --> 00:16:13,840
Actually, I don't have many friends.

295
00:16:13,840 --> 00:16:15,360
Jingu is my only friend.

296
00:16:15,720 --> 00:16:17,320
That's why he brought me here today.

297
00:16:17,320 --> 00:16:18,960
I just joined this class,

298
00:16:19,280 --> 00:16:21,480
and I really want to fit in with everyone.

299
00:16:21,480 --> 00:16:23,200
But I didn't know what you all like,

300
00:16:23,200 --> 00:16:25,280
so I brought these.

301
00:16:25,880 --> 00:16:26,540
From now on,

302
00:16:26,680 --> 00:16:28,560
just tell me what you like from now on.

303
00:16:28,560 --> 00:16:30,760
I'll share whatever I have with you all.

304
00:16:32,040 --> 00:16:33,320
I used to think

305
00:16:33,400 --> 00:16:35,960
pretty girls like you would be hard to approach.

306
00:16:35,960 --> 00:16:38,480
I didn't expect you to have such a great personality.

307
00:16:38,480 --> 00:16:39,560
What do you call this?

308
00:16:39,560 --> 00:16:43,290
This is truly beauty and brains, like a lotus rising from the water.

309
00:16:43,560 --> 00:16:45,320
Gentle and lovely.

310
00:16:45,440 --> 00:16:47,120
No, you flatter me.

311
00:16:47,200 --> 00:16:48,200
I'm not that good.

312
00:16:48,320 --> 00:16:49,760
Actually, I think

313
00:16:50,360 --> 00:16:52,480
the most outstanding girl in your class

314
00:16:52,480 --> 00:16:53,400
is Yuan Bao.

315
00:16:55,600 --> 00:16:57,760
To be liked by so many classmates,

316
00:16:57,800 --> 00:16:59,660
she must have something special.

317
00:17:00,160 --> 00:17:02,840
Yuan Bao, please take care of me in the future.

318
00:17:06,560 --> 00:17:08,040
I was worried before I came.

319
00:17:08,040 --> 00:17:10,119
I didn't expect everyone to be so nice.

320
00:17:10,119 --> 00:17:11,440
Why would you be worried?

321
00:17:11,440 --> 00:17:13,240
Everyone welcomes you, right?

322
00:17:13,400 --> 00:17:14,000
Yes.

323
00:17:14,079 --> 00:17:15,740
We should also thank Gu Xinrui

324
00:17:15,760 --> 00:17:17,000
for the gifts she brought us.

325
00:17:17,000 --> 00:17:19,400
Let's applaud and welcome Gu Xinrui.

326
00:17:19,640 --> 00:17:22,000
Welcome, warm welcome.

327
00:17:22,040 --> 00:17:22,880
Thank you.

328
00:17:22,920 --> 00:17:24,480
Welcome, warm welcome.

329
00:17:24,520 --> 00:17:26,040
You guys are so nice, really.

330
00:17:26,040 --> 00:17:27,160
Thank you.

331
00:17:27,640 --> 00:17:28,800
Really, thank you.

332
00:17:32,520 --> 00:17:33,720
Are you done talking?

333
00:17:34,320 --> 00:17:36,800
Sorry, I might have talked too much.

334
00:17:38,280 --> 00:17:40,480
You, come downstairs with me to order.

335
00:17:48,680 --> 00:17:51,040
Actually, it's just right.

336
00:18:03,640 --> 00:18:05,240
Meng Jingu, what do you mean?

337
00:18:05,560 --> 00:18:06,800
You knew perfectly well that before the summer vacation,

338
00:18:06,800 --> 00:18:07,880
everyone was unhappy

339
00:18:07,880 --> 00:18:09,120
because of the notebook incident.

340
00:18:09,120 --> 00:18:10,850
Yet you brought Gu Xinrui here.

341
00:18:10,880 --> 00:18:12,800
Are you intentionally making things difficult for Yuanbao?

342
00:18:12,800 --> 00:18:15,160
I had no choice but to bring Xinrui along.

343
00:18:16,560 --> 00:18:17,400
No choice?

344
00:18:17,880 --> 00:18:20,040
What, did she threaten you with her life?

345
00:18:20,040 --> 00:18:21,900
I can't explain it to you clearly.

346
00:18:21,960 --> 00:18:22,640
Anyway,

347
00:18:23,160 --> 00:18:24,490
it's not what you think.

348
00:18:24,880 --> 00:18:25,560
Also,

349
00:18:25,960 --> 00:18:27,760
I genuinely came to celebrate Shang Ningyu's birthday

350
00:18:27,760 --> 00:18:29,040
and make everyone happy.

351
00:18:29,040 --> 00:18:31,170
I didn't know Xinrui would say so much.

352
00:18:31,720 --> 00:18:32,680
You didn't know?

353
00:18:33,280 --> 00:18:34,960
Gu Xinrui kept saying

354
00:18:34,960 --> 00:18:36,560
that you wanted to bring her.

355
00:18:36,880 --> 00:18:38,720
You saw the atmosphere just now.

356
00:18:39,360 --> 00:18:41,480
A perfectly good classmate's birthday party

357
00:18:41,480 --> 00:18:43,640
turned into a welcome party for Gu Xinrui.

358
00:18:43,640 --> 00:18:44,520
What is this?

359
00:18:45,120 --> 00:18:46,720
Where does that leave Yuanbao?

360
00:18:46,720 --> 00:18:48,720
I don't want to argue with you today.

361
00:18:48,720 --> 00:18:50,320
I'll clean up the mess I made.

362
00:18:50,440 --> 00:18:52,440
I have nothing more to explain to you.

363
00:18:52,440 --> 00:18:53,770
I'm going to order food.

364
00:18:59,760 --> 00:19:00,920
Autographed?

365
00:19:01,040 --> 00:19:02,000
What are you doing?

366
00:19:02,000 --> 00:19:02,640
Yuanbao.

367
00:19:03,360 --> 00:19:04,160
A toast to you.

368
00:19:04,480 --> 00:19:05,880
If you consider me a friend,

369
00:19:05,880 --> 00:19:06,800
drink this.

370
00:19:08,760 --> 00:19:09,880
If you don't drink,

371
00:19:10,160 --> 00:19:11,520
I'll assume you're still mad at me

372
00:19:11,520 --> 00:19:13,640
over the notebook from the other day,

373
00:19:14,120 --> 00:19:15,520
and I'll be heartbroken.

374
00:19:20,920 --> 00:19:22,200
We can't drink alcohol.

375
00:19:22,200 --> 00:19:23,460
Let's just have water.

376
00:19:24,240 --> 00:19:25,320
You are not kids anymore.

377
00:19:25,320 --> 00:19:27,320
It's just a glass of beer. It's fine.

378
00:19:30,800 --> 00:19:32,960
I have really never drunk alcohol before.

379
00:19:32,960 --> 00:19:35,040
How about we just have soft drinks?

380
00:19:36,400 --> 00:19:36,840
Come on.

381
00:19:36,840 --> 00:19:38,040
Xinrui. Xinrui. Xinrui.

382
00:19:38,040 --> 00:19:39,320
We can't drink alcohol.

383
00:19:39,320 --> 00:19:41,040
Although she usually acts like a tomboy,

384
00:19:41,040 --> 00:19:42,960
she probably hasn't even seen alcohol.

385
00:19:42,960 --> 00:19:44,040
I offered you a toast on purpose

386
00:19:44,040 --> 00:19:45,600
to clear up the misunderstanding.

387
00:19:45,600 --> 00:19:48,080
It's too disrespectful if you don't drink it.

388
00:19:48,080 --> 00:19:49,360
Gu Xinrui, that's enough.

389
00:19:49,360 --> 00:19:50,920
It's meaningless to keep acting up.

390
00:19:50,920 --> 00:19:52,400
No, what did I do?

391
00:19:52,480 --> 00:19:53,940
I just offered her a toast.

392
00:19:54,000 --> 00:19:57,120
Why make it sound like I'm deliberately making things difficult for her?

393
00:19:57,120 --> 00:19:57,780
Aren't you?

394
00:19:58,520 --> 00:19:59,160
Okay.

395
00:20:00,600 --> 00:20:01,960
Soda is fine, right?

396
00:20:04,200 --> 00:20:06,530
Deep feelings, let's see who drinks more.

397
00:20:07,640 --> 00:20:08,440
I'll go first.

398
00:20:18,320 --> 00:20:18,850
Yuanbao.

399
00:20:31,120 --> 00:20:31,880
All right.

400
00:20:35,640 --> 00:20:36,200
Xinrui.

401
00:20:36,200 --> 00:20:37,240
Bei.

402
00:20:41,080 --> 00:20:41,760
Yuanbao, you...

403
00:20:41,760 --> 00:20:42,800
Stop drinking, you two.

404
00:20:42,800 --> 00:20:43,960
That's enough, Xinrui.

405
00:20:43,960 --> 00:20:45,160
That's enough.

406
00:20:45,680 --> 00:20:46,540
That's enough.

407
00:20:50,360 --> 00:20:51,220
That's enough.

408
00:20:56,520 --> 00:20:57,920
Deskmate.

409
00:20:58,080 --> 00:20:58,840
Jingu.

410
00:21:08,760 --> 00:21:09,400
Yuanbao.

411
00:21:10,200 --> 00:21:10,920
I'm sorry.

412
00:21:11,960 --> 00:21:12,960
I'm sorry, guys.

413
00:21:14,240 --> 00:21:16,280
I'll make it up to you next time.

414
00:21:17,000 --> 00:21:17,930
I'm leaving now.

415
00:21:19,480 --> 00:21:20,400
Jingu.

416
00:21:20,840 --> 00:21:21,480
Jingu.

417
00:21:21,760 --> 00:21:22,820
Wait for me, Jingu.

418
00:21:39,480 --> 00:21:41,160
Jingu, what's wrong

419
00:21:41,600 --> 00:21:42,440
with you?

420
00:21:43,600 --> 00:21:44,600
What do you think?

421
00:21:44,840 --> 00:21:46,160
What's wrong with you today?

422
00:21:46,160 --> 00:21:47,920
Why did you keep picking on Yuanbao?

423
00:21:47,920 --> 00:21:49,250
I wasn't picking on her.

424
00:21:49,800 --> 00:21:51,760
I brought her a gift and offered her a toast.

425
00:21:51,760 --> 00:21:53,620
Why do you say I was picking on her?

426
00:21:55,880 --> 00:21:56,440
Jingu.

427
00:21:57,240 --> 00:21:57,960
Jingu.

428
00:21:59,200 --> 00:22:00,930
You said she's just a deskmate.

429
00:22:02,000 --> 00:22:02,960
Are you sure?

430
00:22:06,040 --> 00:22:07,440
No matter what you think,

431
00:22:07,840 --> 00:22:08,600
Xinrui,

432
00:22:09,200 --> 00:22:11,280
I want to tell you clearly today.

433
00:22:12,400 --> 00:22:13,920
We are grown up now.

434
00:22:14,560 --> 00:22:16,420
We can't be like when we were kids.

435
00:22:17,480 --> 00:22:19,200
I have my own life and friends.

436
00:22:19,320 --> 00:22:20,720
Please don't interfere.

437
00:22:21,120 --> 00:22:21,880
Also,

438
00:22:22,680 --> 00:22:24,140
we are brother and sister.

439
00:22:28,840 --> 00:22:29,600
Why?

440
00:22:30,920 --> 00:22:31,880
Why?

441
00:23:15,480 --> 00:23:16,200
Yuanbao.

442
00:23:16,880 --> 00:23:19,240
I had a terrible attitude before,

443
00:23:19,320 --> 00:23:21,160
so please forgive me.

444
00:23:21,600 --> 00:23:23,760
You are a smart

445
00:23:24,040 --> 00:23:25,080
and capable girl.

446
00:23:25,720 --> 00:23:27,650
Although you were clumsy at first,

447
00:23:27,840 --> 00:23:29,680
you quickly got the hang of it.

448
00:23:30,280 --> 00:23:31,120
Here,

449
00:23:31,880 --> 00:23:34,040
I wish you success in your studies

450
00:23:34,480 --> 00:23:35,610
and a bright future.

451
00:23:37,040 --> 00:23:39,160
This milk tea is still very sweet.

452
00:23:39,720 --> 00:23:40,920
But this summer vacation

453
00:23:40,920 --> 00:23:43,360
is full of strange flavors.

454
00:23:44,040 --> 00:23:46,680
I was busy taking extra classes, picking up bottles,

455
00:23:46,680 --> 00:23:48,610
and interning at the milk tea shop.

456
00:23:48,760 --> 00:23:50,520
For some reason, Mutou

457
00:23:50,560 --> 00:23:52,290
suddenly rarely came to see me.

458
00:23:52,760 --> 00:23:54,360
Maybe I was too busy.

459
00:23:55,360 --> 00:23:56,520
I managed to find some free time

460
00:23:56,520 --> 00:23:59,160
and finished watching the TV drama 'Struggle'.

461
00:23:59,160 --> 00:24:01,360
The secret behind Meng Jingu's puzzle

462
00:24:01,600 --> 00:24:03,200
remains a secret.

463
00:24:03,320 --> 00:24:05,040
At Shang Ningyu's birthday party,

464
00:24:05,040 --> 00:24:06,770
Gu Xinrui's sudden appearance

465
00:24:06,840 --> 00:24:08,640
made me feel extra uneasy

466
00:24:08,800 --> 00:24:10,130
about the new semester.

467
00:24:14,480 --> 00:24:15,040
Yuanbao.

468
00:24:16,400 --> 00:24:18,130
The puzzle I gave you last time,

469
00:24:19,240 --> 00:24:20,240
did you finish it?

470
00:24:22,600 --> 00:24:24,680
Puzzle.

471
00:24:25,320 --> 00:24:25,960
Yes.

472
00:24:26,240 --> 00:24:28,680
Oh no. He still remembers it.

473
00:24:29,000 --> 00:24:30,000
What should I say?

474
00:24:31,440 --> 00:24:32,000
Yuanbao.

475
00:24:34,160 --> 00:24:35,160
I finished it.

476
00:24:35,240 --> 00:24:36,160
I finished it.

477
00:24:36,360 --> 00:24:37,000
Then,

478
00:24:37,560 --> 00:24:38,760
the words on the back,

479
00:24:39,440 --> 00:24:40,370
you saw them too?

480
00:24:40,440 --> 00:24:42,960
If I tell him I ruined the puzzle

481
00:24:43,240 --> 00:24:44,280
and couldn't figure out

482
00:24:44,280 --> 00:24:45,960
what the secret behind it is,

483
00:24:46,640 --> 00:24:47,800
will he get angry?

484
00:24:50,360 --> 00:24:51,420
Are you willing to?

485
00:24:53,360 --> 00:24:54,360
Here's the thing.

486
00:24:54,880 --> 00:24:56,120
I think,

487
00:24:56,200 --> 00:24:57,530
since it's your secret,

488
00:24:58,760 --> 00:25:00,360
we better keep it low-key.

489
00:25:02,560 --> 00:25:03,360
Don't worry,

490
00:25:03,480 --> 00:25:05,880
I will definitely keep this secret for you.

491
00:25:06,000 --> 00:25:07,080
My lips are sealed.

492
00:25:10,560 --> 00:25:12,040
What is it? A leaf again?

493
00:25:12,360 --> 00:25:12,840
No.

494
00:25:13,080 --> 00:25:13,880
Let's go back.

495
00:25:17,040 --> 00:25:19,200
What's wrong with Meng Jingu today?

496
00:25:19,320 --> 00:25:20,720
He's looking at me weirdly,

497
00:25:20,720 --> 00:25:22,240
and what he said is strange too.

498
00:25:22,240 --> 00:25:22,770
Yuanbao.

499
00:25:24,040 --> 00:25:24,640
Okay.

500
00:25:34,520 --> 00:25:35,720
What happened to you?

501
00:25:35,960 --> 00:25:37,880
I fell during the city training.

502
00:25:40,920 --> 00:25:42,200
How did you end up like this?

503
00:25:42,200 --> 00:25:42,920
Don't ask.

504
00:25:44,480 --> 00:25:45,240
Mu Qingjun.

505
00:25:45,880 --> 00:25:47,960
Don't let sitting together affect your studies.

506
00:25:47,960 --> 00:25:48,960
Don't worry, sir.

507
00:25:55,400 --> 00:25:56,480
I have an announcement to make.

508
00:25:56,480 --> 00:25:59,000
The autumn sports meet is coming up soon.

509
00:25:59,320 --> 00:26:00,920
Every sophomore class in the school...

510
00:26:00,920 --> 00:26:03,240
we will hold a men's basketball tournament

511
00:26:03,240 --> 00:26:05,320
to help everyone integrate into the class better.

512
00:26:05,320 --> 00:26:06,520
The rules are simple.

513
00:26:06,640 --> 00:26:07,960
The science classes will compete first.

514
00:26:07,960 --> 00:26:10,440
The winner

515
00:26:10,640 --> 00:26:12,080
will play the winner of the humanities classes in the finals.

516
00:26:12,080 --> 00:26:13,440
Some of you might think

517
00:26:13,760 --> 00:26:15,960
it's a waste of time and delays your studies.

518
00:26:15,960 --> 00:26:16,880
But Zhicheng

519
00:26:16,960 --> 00:26:18,220
has always emphasized

520
00:26:18,400 --> 00:26:20,800
comprehensive development in morality, intelligence, physical fitness, aesthetics, and labor.

521
00:26:20,800 --> 00:26:22,480
We will never let you just study all the time.

522
00:26:22,480 --> 00:26:25,140
So, you need to balance your studies and health.

523
00:26:25,160 --> 00:26:25,960
Teacher,

524
00:26:26,600 --> 00:26:27,920
what about us girls?

525
00:26:28,440 --> 00:26:29,700
The girls in each class

526
00:26:29,760 --> 00:26:31,680
need to prepare a cheerleading squad.

527
00:26:31,680 --> 00:26:33,440
Even though cheerleaders don't compete,

528
00:26:33,440 --> 00:26:35,240
I still hope you can do a good job.

529
00:26:35,640 --> 00:26:36,880
Given that some students in our class

530
00:26:36,880 --> 00:26:38,140
in your freshman year,

531
00:26:38,400 --> 00:26:40,600
had experience in the drama competition

532
00:26:40,600 --> 00:26:43,640
I'd like Meng Jingu

533
00:26:43,840 --> 00:26:46,040
and Xing Yaqi to be in charge of this activity.

534
00:26:46,040 --> 00:26:46,920
Do you two have any problems with that?

535
00:26:46,920 --> 00:26:47,720
No problem.

536
00:26:47,880 --> 00:26:49,080
No problem, Mr. Tian.

537
00:26:49,800 --> 00:26:51,200
As for the class monitor,

538
00:26:51,240 --> 00:26:53,360
I'll leave it to Xing Yaqi.

539
00:26:53,480 --> 00:26:54,720
Does anyone have any objections?

540
00:26:54,720 --> 00:26:56,200
No.

541
00:26:56,360 --> 00:26:57,000
Good.

542
00:26:57,400 --> 00:26:59,000
Then we'll have self-study for this class.

543
00:26:59,000 --> 00:27:01,480
Xing Yaqi, organize the class.

544
00:27:01,520 --> 00:27:02,380
Okay, Mr. Tian.

545
00:27:06,280 --> 00:27:07,080
Oh my god.

546
00:27:07,160 --> 00:27:08,400
I didn't expect that in our sophomore year,

547
00:27:08,400 --> 00:27:09,240
our homeroom teacher

548
00:27:09,240 --> 00:27:10,800
would still be Mr. Tian Yong.

549
00:27:10,800 --> 00:27:12,520
And our chemistry teacher is still Da Meili.

550
00:27:12,520 --> 00:27:14,120
What kind of fate is this?

551
00:27:14,160 --> 00:27:15,360
And I heard

552
00:27:15,480 --> 00:27:16,640
that Big Rooster He Qing,

553
00:27:16,640 --> 00:27:17,720
Ms. Xu, and Mr. Zhong

554
00:27:17,720 --> 00:27:18,840
all followed us to sophomore year.

555
00:27:18,840 --> 00:27:19,640
Really?

556
00:27:24,600 --> 00:27:25,730
Don't you love ribs?

557
00:27:25,920 --> 00:27:27,380
I got two portions for you.

558
00:27:27,480 --> 00:27:28,160
Eat.

559
00:27:28,800 --> 00:27:29,860
If it's not enough,

560
00:27:30,400 --> 00:27:31,200
I'll get more.

561
00:27:32,400 --> 00:27:33,200
It's enough.

562
00:27:33,360 --> 00:27:34,480
Thank you.

563
00:27:36,040 --> 00:27:37,370
What are your plans now?

564
00:27:37,560 --> 00:27:38,280
It's fine.

565
00:27:38,360 --> 00:27:40,720
I'll rest for a year and try again next year.

566
00:27:40,720 --> 00:27:41,920
You're so energetic.

567
00:27:42,280 --> 00:27:42,920
Of course.

568
00:27:44,360 --> 00:27:46,560
Any progress with Grandpa and Grandma?

569
00:27:47,280 --> 00:27:50,340
Yuanbao is unwilling, so what progress could there be?

570
00:27:50,440 --> 00:27:51,880
What about you two?

571
00:27:53,080 --> 00:27:54,880
Someone suddenly got in the way.

572
00:27:56,480 --> 00:27:58,210
If it's really good for Yuanbao

573
00:27:58,320 --> 00:28:00,560
and helps her future studies,

574
00:28:01,720 --> 00:28:02,760
I'll back off.

575
00:28:03,560 --> 00:28:05,800
That doesn't sound like the Mu Qingjun I know.

576
00:28:05,800 --> 00:28:07,160
How can you give up?

577
00:28:14,560 --> 00:28:15,720
Miaomiao, did you hear?

578
00:28:15,720 --> 00:28:17,080
Shui transferred schools.

579
00:28:17,080 --> 00:28:18,200
Which Shui?

580
00:28:18,560 --> 00:28:19,440
You know,

581
00:28:19,520 --> 00:28:21,160
the former top guy at Yuhong.

582
00:28:21,200 --> 00:28:23,400
He transferred to Peiying for his senior year.

583
00:28:23,400 --> 00:28:25,040
Is it that Shui

584
00:28:25,120 --> 00:28:27,320
who had a grudge against Mu Qingjun because of Xiong Yuanbao?

585
00:28:27,320 --> 00:28:28,280
Yes, that's him.

586
00:28:28,360 --> 00:28:30,000
I heard that after he transferred schools,

587
00:28:30,000 --> 00:28:31,320
he seemed to have dropped out

588
00:28:31,320 --> 00:28:32,980
and fights outside every day.

589
00:28:33,560 --> 00:28:35,360
Such boys are so annoying.

590
00:28:35,480 --> 00:28:37,680
I think boys should be clean and fair,

591
00:28:37,720 --> 00:28:38,760
love to study,

592
00:28:38,880 --> 00:28:40,200
just like Meng Jingu.

593
00:28:41,080 --> 00:28:42,200
Speaking of Meng Jingu,

594
00:28:42,200 --> 00:28:43,600
I saw him

595
00:28:43,640 --> 00:28:45,320
eating with Xiong Yuanbao in the cafeteria a while ago,

596
00:28:45,320 --> 00:28:47,080
and he kept putting food in her bowl.

597
00:28:47,080 --> 00:28:48,480
Why do boys with good grades

598
00:28:48,480 --> 00:28:50,120
always hang out with girls

599
00:28:50,160 --> 00:28:51,640
who have average grades?

600
00:28:52,600 --> 00:28:54,120
Chang Yu, when do you think

601
00:28:54,120 --> 00:28:56,480
a top student will put food in my bowl?

602
00:28:57,640 --> 00:28:59,400
You'd better study hard.

603
00:28:59,880 --> 00:29:00,480
Let's go.

604
00:29:21,840 --> 00:29:24,520
Are you really quitting the cheerleading performance?

605
00:29:24,520 --> 00:29:27,360
I have no choice. I have to take a vocal grading test.

606
00:29:27,360 --> 00:29:28,920
There's a schedule conflict.

607
00:29:28,920 --> 00:29:31,180
Then who will be the captain if you leave?

608
00:29:31,960 --> 00:29:32,960
Well,

609
00:29:33,960 --> 00:29:36,360
Mr. Tian will probably arrange something.

610
00:29:42,640 --> 00:29:45,120
Summer has quietly passed, leaving behind a little secret.

611
00:29:45,120 --> 00:29:47,040
Today, a kid from Class Seven

612
00:29:47,280 --> 00:29:49,520
passed out after running two laps in PE class.

613
00:29:49,520 --> 00:29:50,400
The doctor said

614
00:29:50,400 --> 00:29:52,200
it's hypoglycemia and a lack of exercise.

615
00:29:52,200 --> 00:29:53,520
Kids these days

616
00:29:53,560 --> 00:29:55,280
really have poor physical fitness.

617
00:29:55,280 --> 00:29:55,960
Exactly.

618
00:29:56,040 --> 00:29:56,440
Let me tell you,

619
00:29:56,440 --> 00:29:58,040
this tradition at our school is really great.

620
00:29:58,040 --> 00:29:59,360
Once kids reach their sophomore year,

621
00:29:59,360 --> 00:30:00,480
the academic pressure is immense.

622
00:30:00,480 --> 00:30:03,210
They need good health to survive these two years.

623
00:30:03,360 --> 00:30:05,200
That's why this basketball tournament

624
00:30:05,200 --> 00:30:06,920
not only builds up the kids' bodies,

625
00:30:06,920 --> 00:30:08,240
but also keeps their enthusiasm high.

626
00:30:08,240 --> 00:30:08,680
Yeah.

627
00:30:08,720 --> 00:30:10,240
I remember when we were in school,

628
00:30:10,240 --> 00:30:12,240
we paid a lot of attention to physical exercise.

629
00:30:12,240 --> 00:30:13,760
Now that we are working,

630
00:30:13,840 --> 00:30:17,240
we are busy and stressed, so we don't have time for it anymore.

631
00:30:21,640 --> 00:30:22,240
All right.

632
00:30:22,800 --> 00:30:24,160
Class, stop writing.

633
00:30:24,920 --> 00:30:26,650
I have an announcement to make.

634
00:30:26,840 --> 00:30:28,170
Class monitor Xing Yaqi

635
00:30:28,280 --> 00:30:29,940
has a vocal grading exam soon,

636
00:30:29,960 --> 00:30:31,820
so she can't join the cheer squad.

637
00:30:31,840 --> 00:30:32,640
I propose

638
00:30:33,040 --> 00:30:34,360
that the cheer captain

639
00:30:34,480 --> 00:30:35,960
be Gu Xinrui.

640
00:30:36,280 --> 00:30:37,240
Any objections?

641
00:30:38,640 --> 00:30:39,440
I disagree.

642
00:30:40,480 --> 00:30:42,120
Mu Qingyun recommended Xiong Yuanbao.
